      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Advanced Race Guide pg. 148</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> strong abjuration <strong>CL</strong> 12th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> shield quality; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>As the <em>guarding </em>property, except as a free action, the wearer selects any number of adjacent allies to receive the shield's bonus. All selected allies receive the same bonus. If a shielded target is ever more than 5 feet from the wearer, the effect ends for that target but not for any other targets.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>shield other</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus</p>",
